{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Your AI agent is bleeding tokens. Right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:94c39deee7d27f17be1094bb33a09d67d58fe8031d6afe9856d319d22abfefa2",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here's the proof: it just flagged a string of text as a real bug, in quotes, inside a test fixture.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5f172e5bda9cbceb1831e72af17467e418e552024e5132629ed2e40b4d2c98d4",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 6.362267573696145,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Then it billed you to investigate. There's a smarter search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e38f6deca67a074093e7e2373bd954e56d6f9628ed93f2d500bfcd75bc966c77",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 28
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Your agent doesn't have it yet. Every AI coding agent has the same blind spot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:20478b182b5664719b9ef1110ad8d19526cf9a420e8c755508d241b02b5c50df",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 38
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Claude Code, Cursor, Copilot \u2014 they all lean heavily on text search for exact code hunts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:556b1cf763c7d9ddb2c2c9a9f69d90ea2d8d685f4c91badaca840c131f2b1c81",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 6.594467120181406,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 53
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "But text search can't tell a real call from a string.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3312d3922fb0083dfa9dd68773ce26be5b12a9695535527e4d9d6b8bef397967",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 69
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "And that's where ast-grep wins. Watch what that costs you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:efd65d32ce799d548adc0ab1821de6d2b3794513e18c7ff57f226267a3c0f8c6",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 80
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Meet ast-grep. It's a smarter search tool that reads your code as code \u2014 not as a wall of text.",
      "checksum": "sha256:47858a2a6cd40b1d3162df2f04750675bd78d74a27876b2e63bc9e3053f06b2b",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 7.198185941043084,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 90
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "A regular search sees characters. ast-grep sees structure: functions, calls, try-catch blocks, the real shape of what you wrote.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cbc39682867fe44a91ee0a6306fbe62d6e5b24661ec6f26612ba04b6a3d23462",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.544943310657596,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 110
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "You hand it to your agent in one config line.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0dfdca22247499c59199b761b41b94bc77896200ab1c6524b7e9e6532ea2fe5b",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 129
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Now your agent stops getting fooled. And stops billing you for the cleanup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0ef3762c5cb52fb12fb394c3c497c5da33adc60f1103859a2956e9340287119d",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 139
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "But how does it actually work? Three steps.",
      "checksum": "sha256:80189520bbb8530989041e14625283e81421858747a4fb3d9a2e6b7c855e3172",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 152
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "First, your code gets parsed by a library called tree-sitter.",
      "checksum": "sha256:49070afeedd2c69c50b05c99d7989d1d14e04d57566f707f8409b6de55fef787",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 160
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "It turns every line into a tree of nodes \u2014 functions, calls, arguments, strings, comments \u2014 each one tagged by what it actually is.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c7544b94c0989c8c22b72208ee5b88ed94776b0e71edc4b1bbae6745931952f3",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 8.359183673469389,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 170
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "That tree is called an AST. Second, ast-grep matches patterns against the tree, not against the text.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cf8e933908cb089744f42e0bea2ca40b67e65bcdf4a6a83738d34e076c595e1e",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 194
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "You write a pattern that looks like real code, with a meta-variable for the parts that change.",
      "checksum": "sha256:702a1e4bc66471c024d0402eb28b60e22012f325bbe78484626dd61a0170f2ca",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 211
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Dollar-sign-VAR matches any single node.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cac3df432a8556415a5cebb0d323179a8c6b79c01268ec23027c51935946bce9",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 228
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Three dollar signs, BODY, matches any list of nodes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c1e70bcbe3c6a0d1401d37858798969e8106d7683133c4a0a6896bdbe74c3223",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 233
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "So if you ask for console-dot-log of dollar-sign-VAR, ast-grep finds every real call \u2014 and skips every string that just looks like one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d7eb2c884640e1c7f562b9fb6dde6936772adfcd4f85e9a2cc5eb74da928d6ec",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 9.520181405895691,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 242
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "A console-dot-log written inside a comment, or inside quoted text, isn't a call node.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fe21db08ebf7e4a514fec229dc1639a7a4f47e63f29778479eddd0e6e41be3bd",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 265
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "It can't match a call pattern. Third, it runs in Rust on every CPU core, so a full codebase scan is fast.",
      "checksum": "sha256:41ea2a940b388e5d301545be4a71cdceebb926d6b8969bfbacbc729380dc2b9b",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 6.733786848072563,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 279
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "That's it. Tree-sitter for the shape. Pattern matching on nodes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b4d5d028523e23705ab360d19b45611012a0ad32d262884ebe5c5286ca4bfd21",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 301
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Multi-core in Rust. Now your agent doesn't get fooled.\n\nWatch your agent waste your money.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bd1c41ff2039d9ad1ce7434c05865494455477c1f40243050f0f74dfc6b328f7",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 311
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "You ask it to clean up dee-bug logs. With the dumb text search, the agent finds 164 matches across 22 files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ff80e6a19221a1dcb03c301df6ae1b43f5d94adde5810c837d1ad15d4a4dd31e",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 7.198185941043084,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 326
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "It opens every one. But here's what's hiding inside dag-executor dot test dot ts: a test fixture passes the literal string console-dot-log-hi.",
      "checksum": "sha256:67523a445073e2188fb418f47802238e1fd97996cc1985b20825a7f8f8e645ef",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 10.402539682539683,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 347
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "It's not a real call. It's just quoted text.",
      "checksum": "sha256:32b0314f5559c536f4c8a7adfbe75e99c7691017e759cd3892db01a7a4492c40",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 369
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "The agent reads the whole file, triages it, and bills you. ast-grep skips it instantly.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0c8608aeb9e5aff5769e6b7ff0854f2de6be0129dcd0856f98caba036f86aea",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 378
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Twelve files, not twenty-two. One example isn't a pattern.",
      "checksum": "sha256:212dbb3561871e60f74a5b85a07a46124a35719b193b6b67bdbdb1a03d88f1cc",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 393
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "So we tested five common searches on the same codebase.",
      "checksum": "sha256:86523971118a2ff2828622cd606e2df23538483763d9a0373fa67d0a0769f0a1",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 402
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "The dumb search over-counted by twenty-six percent on dee-bug logs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2a3f73cbc84651538c73271ca79a5084ac16142af4c7500b8d923cb13cb43dec",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 412
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Nineteen percent on setTimeout. Thirty percent on promise chains.",
      "checksum": "sha256:85589319486c6a552ed6fbfebe83afe9a62bcf6a8b4df897ef02d438f3a95d91",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 422
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "One-hundred-and-twenty-two percent on useState hooks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1803711ad4785faa6c239740dd3407a608a45bfac57262af2cb7bb9fbbe7fa02",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 431
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "That's pure billed waste. Every false hit is a file your agent has to open, scan, and pay for. ast-grep cuts it in half.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8c667a7a36f1f4e858bfb4591c788c8361fdb9dceddb608131c0eb33e9a2469a",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 7.75546485260771,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 436
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Quick word from our affiliate, Hostinger.",
      "checksum": "sha256:74bad3e8093a66c8b2e7c373fee7ff398233efd4796821145855ee3e5a890e29",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 460
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "If you're spinning up your own AI agents or coding sandboxes, Hostinger gives you 10 percent off with the code D I Y smartcode in the description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:359ff94cd1c496acf0774452874dbda57e7d2a880946cbe14170c5738357a849",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 9.148662131519274,
      "word_count": 27,
      "words_offset": 466
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Now, back to ast-grep. Let's translate that into money.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a1978e06494b61b02a05e2185be18efa56551cc9d3af215d65234d7c6833c39b",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 493
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "To audit those 22 files, your agent has to open 22 files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e15f75c755985b28518c50c9ad47e1a1041f774a442be19f3307cf2e6143f9e",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 502
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "That's roughly eleven thousand tokens of context \u2014 call it a cent for a single refactor.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c1cbc14b5987005eb69c7ab57d095525dacf5f17be563808b412627d807dd594",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 514
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Now scale it up. If your team runs fifty refactors a day, thirty days a month, that cent becomes fifteen dollars of pure waste, per developer, just on bad search. ast-grep does the same job in one structured query.",
      "checksum": "sha256:227752aeb1128216a5af1ec1558b3fb5dd93454ae3277c703c9e86f56d4bd567",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 14.44281179138322,
      "word_count": 39,
      "words_offset": 530
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Roughly half the tokens. Your agent stops re-reading files it shouldn't have opened.\n\nBut isn't this just semgrep?",
      "checksum": "sha256:62b20eb240198622f04f945cbc6d7a2b97163f3f90c1894f2239608f7790ff2b",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 569
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Or comby? Or the structural search in my IDE?",
      "checksum": "sha256:5bc10c134e83e645ee0362d27eef17a948c0e95d27ffcae3c5b03bd193f44462",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 587
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "No. Here's why. Semgrep is heavier. It does taint analysis, dataflow, security rules \u2014 powerful, but slow as a CLI, and overkill for everyday refactors.",
      "checksum": "sha256:25f3c52149bb67d55d3e871bdd4afd3443e744716f714b9b5596c6af1187405d",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 9.7059410430839,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 596
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Comby is generic and syntax-aware, but it doesn't give you ast-grep's language-specific AST node precision.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d8397fb6681c2fb56e80f5aa36b5d512be6287e7f1336677da92fcfb97a91792",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 6.919546485260771,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 621
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "GritQL is a multi-paradigm DSL with logic-programming clauses \u2014 a real learning curve before you write your first rule.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a069f31d2c106fada2379745c362b2f7795adbc6ce99386c6fc4bd739b0ab81e",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 8.126984126984127,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 636
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "IntelliJ's structural search is powerful, but it's tied to the JetBrains IDE ecosystem. ast-grep is the lightweight middle.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a046e2b474d345345879693e57c0a53bb4d9f5da45708e3ac7b31dfcdd41845e",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 8.126984126984127,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 655
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "A pipeable command-line tool. Twenty-plus languages out of the box.",
      "checksum": "sha256:462b04017840c327e7adb27dc2a961012103f4c0cd4239acb0aa93e905832b31",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 673
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Easy patterns that look like real code. Fast enough to run inside an agent loop every few seconds.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1665c22562a81187ff3cf95fe7cc3a37deaf403a86629d7f5b3983d867f11050",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 6.222947845804988,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 683
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "That's the point. Not the deepest analyzer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1efdade8489ada0289cff7cb576c501d9542c7df59d6e2859658432dc2d3b0a6",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 701
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Not the broadest text tool. Your agent's daily search hammer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fb2fd702253ddc09a23fc7268e499c1fe80398030ba0e722b94d744731ed59b2",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 708
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "But my agent already has search. Yes \u2014 and it's the dumb one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1cc477b95f05afbe1f10ad6241de864f8b7ed6a5a7ba95e3ec9c2c5f1ec79f91",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 718
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "But Claude Code has Read and Glob. Different jobs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4ed5feb829b00cd0ccd2b4017128e0bd7fb52ce3c5bf699db075f4e6bb6c0f9d",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 731
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Read opens a file you point at. Glob lists files by name.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5fd6b62cd576e5aa609f35f271a3775b19016a6635b5d55d96c9c05d2583de13",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 740
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "Neither one understands code structure. That's what ast-grep adds.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5a6e20fd23651e6655152f9f6459fe70c4d8c0d557d182875dca1fcaa6b93418",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 752
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "But this sounds technical. It isn't. You don't run anything yourself.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5d53b33cfb752a0b0afe113044a34442fb8b2a4c50001187f9fa21d0b7a97aa3",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 761
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "You add one line to your agent's config, and your agent gains the new search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9473dacc1c838277575e7362abbe2af9e530b26de991292dced03173d09cd8d4",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 772
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "The terminal stays untouched.\n\nGiving your agent ast-grep takes two commands.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bfc809570af7632c1c4d753269f080a70244542b2d3091436140be8ea73b2fd5",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 787
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "One \u2014 install the command-line tool: N P M install dash-G at-ast-grep slash C L I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:534a6791a6a25991cc3616dee6a985ba620354925116afa86379486dff5e0111",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 798
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "Two \u2014 install the agent skill: N P X skills add ast-grep slash agent-skill.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f05f17a8439375ae16c425719392f1edeaed45c56c2741ef3460f800ab46bbde",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 5.712108843537415,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 814
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "Then restart Claude Code and tell it explicitly: use ast-grep to find.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c32f9f766b4e0c70e735b0b699a30c4be450b12ceebf8bd196a17c8c92005852",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 828
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "That last part matters \u2014 as of today, you have to name the tool out loud, or the agent will fall back to its old text search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:526b7452e9bf6ff4d3fcadf18a14ff223abc4808b7545374620dffd7cc05ef23",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 7.801904761904762,
      "word_count": 27,
      "words_offset": 840
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "Your agent now has the smart search it should have had from day one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:604216e0e884322e4544b8a941118190746fe2e5b92022bbec2960beaefebe96",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 867
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "So here's the question. Your AI agent burns money on every refactor \u2014 one-hundred-and-twenty-two percent more work than it needs, on real code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f0a30f9242a032bf41de92f162a192f9ed937767625dd14913e0a0c6529aba9a",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 9.009342403628118,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 881
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "Are you fixing that today with one config line?",
      "checksum": "sha256:d74e798c9a344e37d477ce11141f06b838e1c39f989e3e894e937769abaab791",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 904
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "Or accepting the waste? Drop your pick in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5221852b3b397ae42dc0a9f2b576c7b2a4fbe7021ed38257c6e47603b947cb2d",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 913
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "Subscribe for more AI coding deep-dives.",
